{"image_id": "WDC_2014_page_45", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "two years from the closing date of March 8, 2012). In March 2014, we submitted an application to MOFCOM request-", "bbox": [143.8, 140.8, 1094.2, 161.6]}, {"text": "ing that the regulatory restrictions be lifted. At this time, we are awaiting MOFCOM’s response to our application.", "bbox": [143.8, 165.8, 1068.3, 186.6]}, {"text": "For additional information on our acquisition, see Part II, Item 8, Note 15 of the Notes to Consolidated Finan-", "bbox": [185.5, 203.3, 1094.1, 224.1]}, {"text": "cial Statements included in this Annual Report on Form 10-K.", "bbox": [143.8, 228.3, 648.4, 249.1]}, {"text": "Results of Operations", "bbox": [143.8, 278.3, 331.5, 299.1]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2014 Overview", "bbox": [164.6, 315.7, 325.8, 336.6]}, {"text": "In accordance with accounting principles generally accepted in the United States (“U.S. GAAP”), operating", "bbox": [185.5, 353.3, 1094.0, 374.2]}, {"text": "results for Virident, sTec, VeloBit and HGST, which were acquired on October 17, 2013, September 12,", "bbox": [143.8, 378.3, 1094.2, 399.2]}, {"text": "2013, July 9, 2013 and March 8, 2012, respectively, are included in our operating results only after the respective", "bbox": [143.8, 403.3, 1093.9, 424.2]}, {"text": "dates of acquisition.", "bbox": [143.8, 428.4, 303.2, 449.2]}, {"text": "In 2014, our net revenue decreased by 1% to $15.1 billion on hard drive shipments of 249 million units as", "bbox": [185.5, 465.9, 1094.1, 486.7]}, {"text": "compared to $15.4 billion on shipments of 242 million units in 2013. In 2014, 53% of our net revenue was derived", "bbox": [143.8, 490.9, 1094.0, 511.7]}, {"text": "from our enterprise applications, branded products and CE products, as compared to 50% in 2013. Hard drive average", "bbox": [143.8, 515.9, 1094.1, 536.7]}, {"text": "selling price (“ASP”) decreased to $58 in 2014 from $61 in 2013. Gross profit as a percentage of revenue increased to", "bbox": [143.8, 540.9, 1094.1, 561.7]}, {"text": "28.8% in 2014 from 28.4% in 2013. Operating income increased from $1.3 billion in 2013 to $1.8 billion in 2014.", "bbox": [143.8, 565.9, 1094.2, 586.7]}, {"text": "Operating income in 2014 included $95 million of employee termination, asset impairment and other charges and", "bbox": [143.8, 590.9, 1094.2, 611.7]}, {"text": "$52 million of charges related to an arbitration award as compared to $138 million and $681 million for the same", "bbox": [143.8, 615.9, 1094.1, 636.8]}, {"text": "charges in 2013, respectively. As a percentage of net revenue, operating income was 11.8% in 2014 compared to 8.2%", "bbox": [143.8, 640.9, 1094.2, 661.8]}, {"text": "in 2013. Net income in 2014 was $1.6 billion, or $6.68 per diluted share, compared to $980 million, or $3.98 per", "bbox": [143.8, 665.9, 1094.1, 686.8]}, {"text": "diluted share, in 2013.", "bbox": [143.8, 690.9, 326.5, 711.8]}, {"text": "For the September quarter, we expect overall hard drive industry shipments to increase from the June quarter’s", "bbox": [185.5, 728.4, 1094.0, 749.3]}, {"text": "138 million units primarily as a result of seasonality. We expect our revenue in the September quarter to increase", "bbox": [143.8, 753.5, 1094.0, 774.3]}, {"text": "slightly as a result of seasonality and an additional week in our first fiscal quarter of 2015 to realign our fiscal quarter", "bbox": [143.8, 778.5, 1094.0, 799.3]}, {"text": "ends.", "bbox": [143.8, 803.5, 184.9, 824.3]}, {"text": "Summary Comparison of 2014, 2013 and 2012", "bbox": [164.6, 853.4, 519.9, 874.3]}, {"text": "The following table sets forth, for the periods presented, selected summary information from our consolidated", "bbox": [185.5, 891.0, 1093.9, 911.8]}, {"text": "statements of income by dollars and percentage of net revenue (in millions, except percentages):", "bbox": [143.8, 916.0, 909.1, 936.8]}, {"text": "Years Ended", "bbox": [799.8, 948.3, 888.3, 965.0]}, {"text": "June 27, 2014", "bbox": [61